00:10:36.000 --> 00:10:50.000
Coach:  Exactly.  That shows your commitment to their success and creates a more collaborative atmosphere.  What kind of resources do you think might be most helpful for this teacher?

00:10:51.000 --> 00:11:05.000
Maria:  Well, they mentioned feeling overwhelmed by the amount of material in the new curriculum, so maybe I could provide them with a simplified pacing guide or some pre-made lesson plans.

00:11:06.000 --> 00:11:20.000
Coach:  That's a great idea.  You could also offer to connect them with other teachers who have successfully implemented the curriculum. They could share their experiences and offer peer support.

00:11:21.000 --> 00:11:35.000
Maria:  That's a good idea.  I know a few teachers who are really enthusiastic about the new curriculum and would be happy to help.

00:11:36.000 --> 00:11:50.000
