00:12:06.000 --> 00:12:20.000
Coach:  That's a valid concern, Maria.  It's important to frame your offer in a way that empowers the teacher and respects their professional judgment.

00:12:21.000 --> 00:12:35.000
Maria:  How can I do that?

00:12:36.000 --> 00:12:50.000
Coach:  You could say something like, "I know this is a lot to take in, and I want to make sure you have all the support you need. I have some resources that might be helpful, but feel free to use them only if you find them valuable."

00:12:51.000 --> 00:13:05.000
