00:13:06.000 --> 00:13:20.000
Coach:  Exactly.  And you can also frame it as a way to save them time and reduce their workload.  You could say, "These resources might help you streamline your planning and free up some time to focus on other things."

00:13:21.000 --> 00:13:35.000
